  • KIDS Genre has about 127 Shows and DRAMA Genre has 125 Shows.
  • The Most Popular Genre is DOCUMENTARY followed by COMEDY and DRAMA.
  • THIS IS US is the Most Popular Show in the Genre Drama.
  • SIENFELD is the Most Popular Show in the Genre Comedy.
  • TUMBLE LEAF is the Most Popular Show in the Genre Kids.
  • Most of the Shows on Amazon Prime are for 16+ AGE.
  • The Highest Rated Show on Amazon Prime is- "The Test: A New Era for Australia's Team".
  • The Lowest Rated Show on Amazon Prime is- "Ilana Glazer:The Planet is Burning".

Conclusions.

From the above Analysis and Obervations, we can conclude that : -

  • The Audiences are liking the Online content in Amazon Prime.
  • Most of our Audiences are of 16+ Age who love to watch Mature Content and Documentaries.
  • There are a lot of Popular Shows with Higher Number of Seasons and Ratings in this Digital Platform which shows that People love Binge Watching if the Content is good.
  • The Highest IMDB Rating of 9 has been given to the Latest Released Shows in 2020 which shows that the Content has got better with Time.
  • The Content is in Variety of Languages which means there are Worldwide Audiences.
